====== H5957: עָלַם ======

===== Source =====

(Aramaic) corresponding to  H5769 ;

===== Meaning =====

remote time , i.e. the  future  or  past  indefinitely; often adverb,  forever

===== Definitions =====

  - remote time
  - future
  - past
  - forever

===== Usage =====

for (n-)ever (lasting), old.
